Write a PHP program to calculate the factorial of a given positive integer n. The program should use a loop to perform the calculation and then output the result.

<?php
// Taking input from the user
$n = readline("Enter a positive integer: ");

// Initializing the factorial variable
$factorial = 1;

// Calculating the factorial using a loop
for ($i = 1; $i <= $n; $i++) {
    $factorial *= $i;
}

// Outputting the result
echo "The factorial of $n is: $factorial\n";
?>
